/*
 * Parse.l - basic lexical analyzer
 *
 *	Vax/Basic to C++ lexical analyzer
 *
 * Description:
 *
 *	This procedure is used to break Vax/Basic source code
 *	into individual tokens, when are passed on to 'parse.y'.
 *
 */
